ED_Title: Maintenance of international  security – good-neighbourliness, stability and development in South-Eastern Europe
ED_DecisionText: At its 46th plenary meeting, on 7 December 2022, the General Assembly, on the recommendation of the First Committee, (Footnote: A/77/379, para. 7.),  decided to include in the provisional agenda of its seventy-ninth session the item entitled “Maintenance of international security – good-neighbourliness, stability and development in South-Eastern Europe”.
ED_Disclaimer: The final version of decisions adopted during the main part of the session will be contained in document A/77/49 (Vol. II) after editorial review.
